## Quality Bar
- TypeScript throughout — no `any` unless unavoidable
- Loading states on all async data (skeleton loaders, not spinners)
- Error boundaries on chart and trade panel
- Mobile responsive: landing page must look great on 375px; trade page collapses to tabs on mobile
- No placeholder data on launch — everything pulls from real APIs
- Lighthouse performance score target: 85+
- Deploy to Vercel with all env vars set

